HAMLToe
=======

HAMLToe is a simple haml to html translator that allows for editing with an on the fly preview of the resulting html.

Based heavily on parts of PageDown (https://code.google.com/p/pagedown/) and uses the haml.js script from
http://haml-html-coffeecup-javascript-coffeescript-converter.smullindesign.com/ (https://github.com/uglyog) with some
minor modifications.

Released under the MIT License (http://www.opensource.org/licenses/MIT).

Live demo available at https://rawgithub.com/rjohnst/hamltoe/master/demo.html
